-- Einhorn's Greenlight Capital finds Micron leaker, drops case
-- By Jonathan Stempel in New York
-- Mon Mar 24, 2014 03:57PM EDT
-- None



NEW YORK, March 24 (Reuters) - Greenlight Capital Inc, the hedge fund overseen by David Einhorn, has identified a blogger who disclosed its stake in Micron Technology Inc <MU.O> before it was officially announced, and has dropped a legal case seeking to force the website Seeking Alpha to reveal the blogger's name.

